{"tid":2449170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（讓領導先走）據報中方已下令國企撤離在緬甸非必要工作人員","createTime":"2021-03-16T12:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T17:11:31.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ecd57059771930d739c9863d7fa88ea91035560d","tid":2449170,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T12:40:16.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】緬甸反軍事政變示威持續，軍警開槍驅散，中方據報已下令國企撤走非必要工作人員。<br />\n<br />\n在最大城市仰光，軍警繼續武力鎮壓示威，有民眾聲稱連續第二日無法用手機的流動網絡上網。仰光市內多處起火，網上消息指，再有示威者中槍不治。第二大城市曼德勒亦有軍警開火，有民居玻璃窗留有彈孔。<br />\n<br />\n據報，當局認為著名投資者索羅斯旗下一個基金會涉嫌資助示威者，已拘捕一名幹事。<br />\n<br />\n伊洛瓦底省有兩名警員因為反政變被捕，判處一年監禁。<br />\n<br />\n早前有中國工廠被人縱火破壞，《南華早報》引述消息報道，中方已下令中資企業撤走在緬甸的非必要員工。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=427618\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D427618&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixcg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=340a66aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D427618&h=3e092bfd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=427618</a>"},{"pid":"9eabb282275133b89f1bd23310ef117f10907062","tid":2449170,"uid":19012,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T12:41:58.000Z","msg":"報得出黎 即刻已經神早走灑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n未走個堆係 可以替換既奴隸"},{"pid":"f8a6e18471b08684338fd51210eb1b5538b92546","tid":2449170,"uid":53705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:10:45.000Z","msg":"非必要工作人員 = 官員家屬, 親人, 高層領導<br />\n<br />\n低層員工 繼續留係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c517ed1a08f2eab6daf5f03aa02e3c8f1227a84c","tid":2449170,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:18:55.000Z","msg":"吳京出動未"},{"pid":"54dc30767efdaf36b0c27c1fa83c856edd9b17f9","tid":2449170,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af78f07dfc34fefdf23e6374786e8bbb8bf166b","tid":2449170,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T15:41:26.000Z","msg":"留得底都有間諜任務"},{"pid":"f6bfce5a8e2a11071fef3ea402bd2ac94ce194cf","tid":2449170,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T17:11:31.000Z","msg":"走曬無得排支喎"}]}